# NAME: Telegram IP / ASN
# AUTHOR: JovanyKoch
# UPDATED: 2026-06-03
# TYPE: Loon Ruleset
# DESC: Telegram main rule set, giving priority to IP-CIDR / IP-CIDR6 / IP-ASN, with a small number of domain names used for login, link preview and pre-matching.
# NOTE: It is recommended to use R in the main configuration ULE-SET,telegram.list,Telegram,no-resolve。

# Telegram IPv4
IP-CIDR,91.108.4.0/22,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,91.108.8.0/22,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,91.108.56.0/22,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,95.161.64.0/20,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,149.154.160.0/22,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,149.154.164.0/22,no-resolve

# Telegram IPv6
IP-CIDR6,2001:67c:4e8::/48,no-resolve

# Telegram ASN
IP-ASN,62041,no-resolve
IP-ASN,62014,no-resolve
IP-ASN,59930,no-resolve
IP-ASN,211157,no-resolve
IP-ASN,44907,no-resolve
